  "config": {
    "title": "HeatwaveProof",
    "details": "\nHeatwaveProof DApp with two main sections:\n\n1. ADMIN PANEL (🚨 Publish Alert) — visible only to the contract owner:\n   - City (text input)\n   - Temperature in °C (number input with decimal — multiply by 10 before sending, e.g., 37.5 → 375, stored as int256)\n   - Humidity % (number 0–100, stored as uint8)\n   - UV Index (number 0–20, stored as uint8)\n   - Risk Level (dropdown 1–5: 1=Low, 2=Moderate, 3=High, 4=Very High, 5=Extreme, stored as uint8)\n   - Safety Advice (textarea, stored as string)\n   - Submit button: \"🚨 Publish Heatwave Alert\" calls publishAlert(city, temperature*10, humidity, uvIndex, riskLevel, safetyAdvice)\n\n2. PUBLIC PANEL (📋 View Alerts):\n   - Total alert count at top (calls getTotalAlerts())\n   - \"Latest Alert\" card showing all fields from getLatestAlert() — temperature divided by 10 to show actual °C\n   - Risk level shown as colored badge: 1=green, 2=yellow, 3=orange, 4=red, 5=dark red\n   - City search input + \"Search\" button calls getAlertsByCity(city) and shows results as cards\n   - Timestamps formatted as human-readable dates\n\nSTYLE:\n- Emergency/warning theme: dark background (#0d0d0d or similar), orange/red accents (#ff6b35, #ff3333)\n- Glowing/alert aesthetic for cards (subtle orange border glow)\n- Clear visual hierarchy with section headers\n- Mobile-friendly responsive layout\n- Risk level badge colors: 1=#22c55e (green), 2=#eab308 (yellow), 3=#f97316 (orange), 4=#ef4444 (red), 5=#7f1d1d (dark red)\n- Timestamp formatted as human-readable date (e.g., \"Jan 15, 2025, 3:42 PM\")\n- Contract address is a placeholder — show a banner/notice if address is not set\n",
